text: Villeneuve-Saint-Nicolas is a former commune in the Eure-et-Loir department in northern France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Les Villages-Vovéens.Arrêté préfectoral 30 September 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in France Category:Communes in Eure-et-Loir
title: Villeneuve-Saint-Nicolas
